{"tid":1632013,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"某部分勇武當左自己係黑社會??","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:07.000Z","uid":251206,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6973922b313a355363f7e5bb0e55fa2e42dabd40","tid":1632013,"uid":251206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"好玩?好型?我講緊某d行為，唔係話左全部"},{"pid":"9ebcba280fb4c580b1ac78f8ae9341e938e2f9d2","tid":1632013,"uid":76745,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:52.000Z","msg":"blocked"},{"pid":"43f3dbd0274c4330abe72ebc2c111a0e6b3f6473","tid":1632013,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"a56e66c636688996fac02db274aa31c64c1dd1c6","tid":1632013,"uid":250164,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"起底 不推文"},{"pid":"54df74cf171f521f63dcd0af4b8e10e1431159ee","tid":1632013,"uid":251206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:08.000Z","msg":"比我感覺係咁"},{"pid":"dc69fa2fbcfcea771c642a7fe4f025849dbf631e","tid":1632013,"uid":263618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:50.000Z","msg":"咁有啲本身真係黑社會呀嘛<br />\n但冇問題 我哋要跟返個大原則 黑先裝修，其他做下文宣算，唔該曬"},{"pid":"af3a80e515a7b61cad5bf5eedc02d5e7725b6fee","tid":1632013,"uid":78304,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"又一件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nblocked"},{"pid":"f07d674ecd35a6e304f12dd9f12891da83c0ebbe","tid":1632013,"uid":72777,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"你覺得前線有咩問題, 請直接提出<br />\n某D行為即係咩行為呀? <br />\n你咁講野同謾罵有咩分別?<br />\n連登已經好多無謂POST, 唔該唔好再增加垃圾"},{"pid":"d76ecf7b1989686fb767d0be08a73fbbf5474444","tid":1632013,"uid":195252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:33.000Z","msg":"咩叫黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殺人強姦賣毒品就係黑社會，手足頂多都係玩下火姐。<br />\n<br />\n拉！"},{"pid":"a185e039058b9c01e5ac23f0beab2c7f0536d800","tid":1632013,"uid":251206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d76ecf7b1989686fb767d0be08a73fbbf5474444","tid":1632013,"uid":195252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:33.000Z","msg":"咩叫黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殺人強姦賣毒品就係黑社會，手足頂多都係玩下火姐。<br />\n<br />\n拉！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"唔岩政件就圍人打人?人多惡哂?"},{"pid":"c67a704fcd1217820383a68217800ae6c5cceaf0","tid":1632013,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾post"},{"pid":"9caf763a320f0a50af221c567c70d406edbe9fe1","tid":1632013,"uid":8938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"請善用起底同不推文功能"},{"pid":"6cab17c655a199c059cf04c8eb4faf978cba7759","tid":1632013,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">善用起底功能同不推文回覆</span>"},{"pid":"cc8ae36c4bbdf7d83b20d1de6a19308b59e906cf","tid":1632013,"uid":137629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:07.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 五毛狗"}]}